name: sense #2: it's complicated
description:
be prepared to accept whatever life throws at you. nobody said it would be easy. it can be overwhelming at times. when you step back and reflect on the series of events that led to this point, a beautiful symphony of feelings emerges. your impact on the universe is undeniable. 

the sense collection is based on my own life experiences, along with those common feelings that we all experience along the journey.
